title: Episode 4 - Super V GDP, Senate Map Update, and the Mystery of Miles Taylor
description:
It's another action packed episode of Ruthless!  This time Josh and Comfortably Smug discuss the booming Super V Trump Recovery, Josh runs us through the senate election map, and Smug reveals the true identity of Anonymous, who Josh stuffs into a locker.  Ladies and gentlemen, let's get Ruthless.
